{"title":"AngularJS中的运行块(run)","slug":"AngularJS中的运行块(run)","date":"2017-09-21T12:18:49.968Z","updated":"2017-09-21T14:17:00.157Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-运行块\"><a href=\"#1-运行块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 运行块.\"></a>1. 运行块.</h2><ul>\n<li>ng内置的服务,如果我们想要使用.让服务脱离控制器执行.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-让服务脱离控制器执行\"><a href=\"#2-让服务脱离控制器执行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.让服务脱离控制器执行.\"></a>2.让服务脱离控制器执行.</h2><ul>\n<li>模块对象提供一个方法,叫做run,直接使用服务.而不依赖于控制器.<ul>\n<li>参数: 数组,前面写上要使用的服务的名称,后面1个回调</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"实现：\"><a href=\"#实现：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现：\"></a>实现：</h2><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">app.run([<span class=\"string\">\"$rootScope\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">$rootScope</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    $rootScope.age = <span class=\"number\">100</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;]);</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">app.controller(<span class=\"string\">\"hmCtrl\"</span>,[<span class=\"string\">\"$scope\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">$scope</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    $scope.name = <span class=\"string\">\"jack\"</span></div><div class=\"line\">&#125;]);</div><div class=\"line\">app.controller(<span class=\"string\">\"hmCtrl\"</span>,[<span class=\"string\">\"$rootScope\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">$rootScope</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;])</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote>\n","categories":[{"name":"Angular","path":"api/categories/Angular.json"}],"tags":[]}